I was scrolling through my feed about a month or so ago when I noticed that one of my all time favorite rappers who I’ve been listening too for about 10 years now, @chriswebby 🕸🔥🚀 who I’ve had the chance to write an article about with @hempconnoisseur 2 years ago and photograph during a few of his Colorado shows, is an epic overall artist and one of the most witty and lyrical rappers in hip-hop (in my opinion). He decided to use one of the photos I took of him during the show in Colorado Springs on 4/19 for his European tour flyer and I was fucking shocked. My feelings of extreme gratitude doesn’t really hit the mark, I’m just beyond stoked ❤️📸🔥🙌🏻 and I wanted to share the tour flyer and you can swipe right to see the original photo used. 🙏🏻❤️🤯📸🕸🙌🏻🔥🚀 I’ve wanted to write this up for a couple weeks but didn’t take the time to sit down and type it out. Much love to @chriswebby and his whole team, I hope the tour across Europe is epic. 🙏🏻❤️🚀🚀🚀🚀🚀🔥📸😤
.
